in front of me to save me.

8
00:01:34,928 --> 00:01:38,389
{\an8}<i>And I'll make whoever did this</i>
<i>to Mikoy pay.</i>

9
00:01:39,182 --> 00:01:41,518
{\an8}Is it my fault there
was an emergency at work?

10
00:01:42,811 --> 00:01:46,731
