15
00:01:58,618 --> 00:02:00,328
{\an8}You really have some nerve, don't you?

16
00:02:03,623 --> 00:02:05,792
{\an8}You just disappeared into thin air.

17
00:02:06,376 --> 00:02:08,294
{\an8}And you brought a guy?

18
00:02:08,837 --> 00:02:09,921
{\an8}For what?

19
