99
00:12:27,913 --> 00:12:29,331
<i>Where are we?</i>

100
00:12:46,056 --> 00:12:50,644
<i>Last time, you underestimated</i>
<i>your enemies.</i>

101
00:12:51,228 --> 00:12:55,566
<i>Are you sure you've</i>
<i>finished them off this time?</i>

102
00:13:04,950 --> 00:13:06,619
