You never fought for us!

122
00:15:08,073 --> 00:15:09,241
Oh?

123
00:15:09,325 --> 00:15:12,161
Right? You have nothing to say?

124
00:15:12,244 --> 00:15:14,580
I did everything to make us work.

125
00:15:14,663 --> 00:15:18,542
But I'm starting to believe
