126
00:15:19,126 --> 00:15:22,546
Ben, let's not relitigate our past.

127
00:15:23,547 --> 00:15:25,966
This isn't the right time
or place to talk about that.

128
00:15:26,050 --> 00:15:28,844
If not now, when?

129
00:15:28,928 --> 00:15:31,639
If not here, then where?

130
00:15:32,848 --> 00:15:33,682
Huh?

131
00:15:56,288 --> 00:15:57,456
Mikoy?

132
00:15:59,124 --> 00:16:00,250
Mikoy!

133
00:16:00,334 --> 00:16:01,502
Mikoy!

134
