140
00:16:33,325 --> 00:16:34,618
- My son!
- My son!

141
00:16:35,828 --> 00:16:38,288
- Son!
- Tess! Tess!

142
00:16:38,372 --> 00:16:40,082
Tess! Tess! Tess!

143
00:16:40,165 --> 00:16:41,625
- Oops, sorry.
- My son!

144
00:16:41,709 --> 00:16:43,419
Mikoy survived the bullet wound.

145
00:16:43,502 --> 00:16:45,462
He'll die because you're heavy.

146
00:16:48,882 --> 00:16:50,592
Are you saying I'm heavy?

147
00:16:52,970 --> 00:16:54,638
Love, you really are heavy.

148
00:16:54,722 --> 00:16:55,889
In love.

149
00:16:56,598 --> 00:16:57,850
There it is.

150
00:16:58,475 --> 00:17:00,644
- So silly.
- Of course, in love.

151
00:17:01,520 --> 00:17:02,479
Son.

152
00:17:03,147 --> 00:17:04,898
Don't ever do that again, okay?

153
00:17:05,482 --> 00:17:09,778
Because I might die
from worrying about you. Huh?

154
00:17:10,404 --> 00:17:12,239
Mom, don't worry.

155
00:17:13,198 --> 00:17:15,826
It will never happen again.

156
00:17:17,411 --> 00:17:18,245
Really?

157
00:17:18,829 --> 00:17:20,039
I promise.

158
00:17:20,998 --> 00:17:23,500
I will never let anyone hurt you again.

159
00:17:26,545 --> 00:17:30,215
Whoever tries, I'll chop them into pieces!

160
00:17:31,008 --> 00:17:32,092
Wow!

161
00:17:32,176 --> 00:17:34,178
Chiara is scary!

162
00:17:52,071 --> 00:17:54,615
Our suspect was able to enter the hospital

163
00:17:54,698 --> 00:17:56,492
