<i>to be a hospital staff</i>

166
00:18:00,329 --> 00:18:02,289
<i>to move that easily.</i>

167
00:18:02,372 --> 00:18:04,541
<i>And he or she is not only physically good.</i>

168
00:18:04,625 --> 00:18:08,921
<i>He or she is also very, very smart, too.</i>

169
00:18:10,214 --> 00:18:13,759
<i>He or she made sure</i>
<i>no trace was left behind.</i>

170
00:18:20,599 --> 00:18:24,103
<i>Because he or she</i>
<i>physically destroyed the drives.</i>

171
00:18:38,033 --> 00:18:39,910
With whatever kind of trickery,

172
00:18:40,452 --> 00:18:44,123
