information from Attorney Salazar.

173
00:18:44,748 --> 00:18:47,251
That's probably how she found
the Sinigang Cartel hideout.

174
00:18:47,334 --> 00:18:49,753
And there is a very real possibility

175
00:18:49,837 --> 00:18:51,839
