who hit the hideout

176
00:18:51,922 --> 00:18:58,220
and virtually took down the entire
Sinigang Cartel leadership.

177
00:19:04,143 --> 00:19:07,271
I strongly suspect she knows a lot
of secrets about the Moraviano.

178
00:19:11,316 --> 00:19:12,359
But, Bok.

179
00:19:13,861 --> 00:19:18,115
We know how dangerous this operator is.

180
00:19:18,824 --> 00:19:20,742
So, we all need to be careful, Bok.

181
00:19:20,826 --> 00:19:21,827
All of us.

182
00:19:21,910 --> 00:19:23,871
Because if we're not careful,

183
00:19:23,954 --> 00:19:25,581
