191
00:19:56,570 --> 00:19:57,821
Yes!

192
00:19:59,031 --> 00:20:00,199
But you know…

193
00:20:01,158 --> 00:20:06,997
If you're the one tickling me,
I'd get shot every day.

194
00:20:12,044 --> 00:20:14,129
Do you know how close
my heart was to exploding

195
00:20:14,213 --> 00:20:16,632
