199
00:20:39,613 --> 00:20:42,532
If you hadn't played the hero,
then I would've just been kidnapped.

200
00:20:43,116 --> 00:20:45,410
Do you think
I would let you get kidnapped?

201
00:20:45,994 --> 00:20:47,537
No one is taking you from me.

202
00:20:55,504 --> 00:20:56,922
I already love you.

203
00:20:57,005 --> 00:20:58,882
You don't need to act cute anymore.

204
00:21:01,009 --> 00:21:02,386
Are you sure?

205
00:21:08,976 --> 00:21:10,852
Of course, I love you so much.

206
00:21:15,691 --> 00:21:17,985
Come here.

207
00:21:23,824 --> 00:21:27,536
I know, but I really don't remember much
about that event.

208
00:21:28,245 --> 00:21:31,707
The last thing I remember
is heading to the venue.

209
00:21:33,500 --> 00:21:37,170
That's normal for gunshot victims.

210
00:21:37,796 --> 00:21:41,341
Usually hazy or foggy memories
because of trauma.

211
00:21:41,425 --> 00:21:43,260
But it's okay. It will come back.

212
00:21:46,513 --> 00:21:49,933
You know, I can only imagine
your mother's trauma.

213
00:21:50,767 --> 00:21:52,269
How is she?

214
00:21:55,147 --> 00:21:56,773
She's okay.

215
00:21:56,857 --> 00:21:59,401
She was released by the kidnappers.

216
00:21:59,484 --> 00:22:01,611
Dad paid the ransom immediately.

217
00:22:03,071 --> 00:22:04,698
Chiara, were they really just kidnappers?

218
00:22:06,742 --> 00:22:08,577
Does your dad have no enemies?

219
00:22:14,291 --> 00:22:15,625
I don't know.

220
00:22:21,798 --> 00:22:26,303
So, even you
are under tight watch in this building.

221
00:22:27,220 --> 00:22:29,973
And you, you need to be careful, too.

222
00:22:31,600 --> 00:22:33,435
Because if something happens to you,

223
00:22:36,146 --> 00:22:38,106
