224
00:22:39,274 --> 00:22:41,193
Nothing will happen to me.

225
00:22:42,319 --> 00:22:43,695
Not while you're here.

226
00:22:48,283 --> 00:22:49,409
Right?

227
00:22:58,668 --> 00:23:03,006
CHICKEN BALL
HOTDOG

228
00:23:04,800 --> 00:23:06,009
