with our mom and dad.

232
00:23:15,102 --> 00:23:17,604
{\an8}Hey! So you're a big deal, huh?

233
00:23:17,687 --> 00:23:20,315
{\an8}Your family is connected to the Valtrovis!

234
00:23:20,816 --> 00:23:24,027
