238
00:23:33,662 --> 00:23:36,706
{\an8}Nowhere! I just read it on Reddit.

239
00:23:37,582 --> 00:23:38,917
Reddit. Reddit.

240
00:23:39,000 --> 00:23:41,461
Don't just believe everything you see.

241
00:23:41,545 --> 00:23:43,672
There's a lot of fake news these days.

242
00:23:43,755 --> 00:23:45,841
{\an8}Why are you so defensive?

243
00:23:45,924 --> 00:23:49,427
You know that it's serious
and traumatic for my family.

244
00:23:53,557 --> 00:23:55,517
My brother almost died.

245
00:23:55,600 --> 00:23:57,936
