to be the subject of online conspiracies.

247
00:24:04,401 --> 00:24:07,863
We are real people affected by that chaos!

248
00:24:10,532 --> 00:24:13,326
Sorry. You're right.

249
00:24:13,994 --> 00:24:15,579
I'm so insensitive.

250
00:24:16,663 --> 00:24:18,123
I didn't realize.

251
00:24:18,790 --> 00:24:19,791
Sorry.

252
00:24:21,626 --> 00:24:22,711
This is good!

253
00:24:23,420 --> 00:24:24,462
But

254
00:24:25,672 --> 00:24:29,259
how did you know that something bad
happened to my brother?

255
00:24:30,218 --> 00:24:31,261
Also,

256
00:24:32,387 --> 00:24:33,889
who was that you called?

257
00:24:34,389 --> 00:24:35,640
From a police officer.

258
00:24:35,724 --> 00:24:37,267
You know someone in the police?

259
00:24:40,312 --> 00:24:42,022
Come here. Chiara, have you eaten?

260
00:24:42,105 --> 00:24:44,649
- Here, eat my porridge first.
- Thank you.

261
00:24:44,733 --> 00:24:46,443
- That's good.
- Okay, dear, this is for you.

262
00:24:46,526 --> 00:24:48,403
Oh, I'm good.

263
00:24:48,486 --> 00:24:49,863
How is Mikoy?

264
00:24:50,447 --> 00:24:52,824
Oh, he's resting. He's okay, Mom.

265
00:24:52,908 --> 00:24:54,367
Okay.

266
00:24:54,451 --> 00:24:56,912
Well, good thing
he has no internal injuries.

267
00:24:56,995 --> 00:24:59,039
But he still needs to move around.

268
00:24:59,122 --> 00:25:02,459
So his bones won't get stiff.

269
00:25:03,585 --> 00:25:06,046
We also decided Mario and I

270
00:25:06,129 --> 00:25:11,343
will stay here for a few days
to help you take care of Mikoy.

271
00:25:13,720 --> 00:25:15,305
Honestly,

272
00:25:16,723 --> 00:25:18,725
I feel a bit guilty.

273
00:25:19,226 --> 00:25:23,396
If it weren't for me,
none of this would have happened.

274
00:25:23,980 --> 00:25:26,733
It should've been me, not Mikoy.

275
00:25:27,567 --> 00:25:29,236
Come here.

276
00:25:30,695 --> 00:25:32,072
You know, child.

277
00:25:32,155 --> 00:25:34,658
Don't blame yourself anymore.

278
00:25:35,242 --> 00:25:37,577
You're not the one who shot Mikoy.

279
00:25:38,453 --> 00:25:42,874
And you're not the villain in this story.

280
00:25:43,541 --> 00:25:44,584
Correct.

281
00:26:41,850 --> 00:26:46,104
<i>Out of all people,</i>
<i>why were they targeted by the gang?</i>

282
00:26:46,187 --> 00:26:48,356
It reminded me of what you told me before,

283
00:26:48,440 --> 00:26:52,193
that you had a bad feeling
when Mikoy met the Valtrovi family.

284
00:26:52,277 --> 00:26:53,361
<i>I'm sorry, Angelito,</i>

285
00:26:53,445 --> 00:26:55,655
<i>I couldn't stop myself from overhearing</i>

286
00:26:55,739 --> 00:26:59,242
<i>your conversation</i>
<i>with your Dad about syndicates.</i>

287
00:26:59,326 --> 00:27:01,286
<i>What if it's true</i>
<i>and it's not just a gossip?</i>

288
00:27:01,369 --> 00:27:02,996
I also have a reliable source

289
00:27:03,079 --> 00:27:06,916
that the Valtrovis are connected
to a syndicate.

290
00:27:08,001 --> 00:27:09,085
When we started investigating,

291
00:27:09,169 --> 00:27:12,172
I asked if they could alert us
of any Central Europeans

292
00:27:12,255 --> 00:27:14,007
with a strong military background.

293
00:27:15,550 --> 00:27:17,385
<i>He became well-known</i>
<i>when he was deployed to Afghanistan.</i>

294
00:27:17,469 --> 00:27:20,805
<i>With so called Noční Řezník,</i>
<i>or "The Butcher of the Night".</i>

295
00:27:20,889 --> 00:27:23,475
No one will hurt Mikoy.

296
00:27:23,558 --> 00:27:29,230
I will not let anyone hurt my loved ones.

297
00:27:35,028 --> 00:27:36,279
<i>What does she want?</i>

